Package: EurostatEnergyIDA
Title: Energy Decomposition Analysis Dashboard for European Countries
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Loic", "", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny dashboard for Index Decomposition Analysis (IDA) 
    of energy consumption across European countries. Analyzes energy consumption 
    decomposition using LMDI methodology for industry (by GVA), transport (by VKM), 
    and residential sectors. Data sourced from Eurostat.
